\">\n                            jump to other results\n                        </a></div></div><ol class=\"senses_multiple\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" hclass=\"sense\" sensenum=\"1\" ox5000=\"y\" htag=\"li\" cefr=\"c1\" id=\"inspection_sng_1\"><span class=\"sensetop\" hclass=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\"><div class=\"symbols\" htag=\"div\" hclass=\"symbols\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/oxford3000-5000?dataset=english&amp;list=ox5000&amp;level=c1\"><span class=\"ox5ksym_c1\">&nbsp;</span></a></div></span><span class=\"def\" hclass=\"def\" htag=\"span\">an official visit to a school, factory, etc. in order to check that rules are being obeyed and that standards are acceptable</span><ul class=\"examples\" hclass=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">Regular <span class=\"cl\">inspections</span> are <span class=\"cl\">carried out</span> at the prison.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">The head went on a <span class=\"cl\">tour of inspection</span> of all the classrooms.</span></li></ul><div class=\"collapse\" htag=\"div\" hclass=\"collapse\"><span class=\"unbox\" id=\"inspection_unbox_1\" unbox=\"extra_examples\"><span class=\"box_title\">Extra Examples</span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">A standard home-inspection report summarizes the condition of the house.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Following an on-site inspection, the surveyor prepared a written report on the property.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Nursing agencies are subject to inspection by the health authority.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">The architect is carrying out a thorough inspection of the building.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">The hotel passed its annual inspection.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">Th